Name: Category
Description: ID of the folder that an item is located in.

Name: Client
Description: Specifies the account ownership and context of an object.

Name: CorrelationID
Description: Identifies correlation of objects across several requests.

Name: CreatedDate
Description: Read-only date and time of the object's creation.

Name: CustomerKey
Description: User-supplied unique identifier for an object within an object type.

Name: Description
Description: Describes and provides information regarding the object.

Name: ID
Description: Read-only legacy identifier for an object. Not supported on all objects.

Name: ModifiedDate
Description: Last time object information was modified.

Name: Name
Description: Name of the object or property.

Name: ObjectID
Description: System-controlled, read-only text string identifier for object.

Name: Owner
Description: Describes account ownership of subscriber in an on-your-behalf account.

Name: PartnerKey
Description: Unique identifier provided by partner for an object. This property is accessible only via API.

Name: PartnerProperties
Description: A collection of metadata supplied by the client and stored by the system. These properties are accessible only via API.

Name: Subscribers
Description: Indicates subscribers associated with an object.
